title: #230 Burrito Bitch
description:
It’s a huge Tuesday’s as Mark & Joe try and figure out if dogs can have missionary sex (the jury is still out) before recapping their huge trip to Denver with Ari Shaffir & Sean Patton where they annoy the staff at a Colorado Avalanche game, take an intimate pedicab ride and have what may be the biggest breakthrough with Chipotle yet! Check it out!
